{"type":"message","id":"9fed4bb8","parentId":"c510d45b","timestamp":"2026-03-29T20:25:02.942Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:0bb637bb-765d-4c8a-b721-260619faf16f Tobias Task Watchdog] Run the Tobias task watchdog. Read C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\task_watchdog\\README.md for context. Execute python C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\task_watchdog\\watchdog.py, inspect its JSON output, and follow this rule strictly: if notifications is empty, reply with exactly NO_REPLY and nothing else. If there are notifications, rewrite each one in clean human Portuguese, concise but informative, and deliver them. Do not send silent confirmations. Do not explain empty scans. Do not invent status.\nCurrent time: Sunday, March 29th, 2026 — 17:25 (America/Sao_Paulo) / 2026-03-29 20:25 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1774815902854}}
{"type":"message","id":"18204222","parentId":"9fed4bb8","timestamp":"2026-03-29T20:25:05.121Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"O usuário quer que eu execute um watchdog de tarefas. Vou:\n1. Ler o README.md do task_watchdog para entender o contexto\n2. Executar o script python\n3. Analisar o output JSON\n4. Se notifications está vazio → responder com exatamente \"NO_REPLY\" e nada mais\n5. Se há notifications → reescrever em português claro, conciso e informativo\n\nVou começar lendo o README.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01WY87gcuwS1t9LDR7bsypgF","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\task_watchdog"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-haiku-4-5","usage":{"input":10,"output":193,"cacheRead":15639,"cacheWrite":740,"totalTokens":16582,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.000965,"cacheRead":0.0015639000000000002,"cacheWrite":0.000925,"total":0.0034639000000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774815903027,"responseId":"msg_01RpNTamzT9CZPWppsiAYTY8"}}
