{"type":"message","id":"522fa63d","parentId":"f18254e7","timestamp":"2026-03-29T20:25:06.604Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Let me read the README file directly:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01QsW5MMo5YN3VRbfjwXXtZq","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\task_watchdog\\README.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-haiku-4-5","usage":{"input":5,"output":81,"cacheRead":15639,"cacheWrite":683,"totalTokens":16408,"cost":{"input":0.0000049999999999999996,"output":0.00040500000000000003,"cacheRead":0.0015639000000000002,"cacheWrite":0.00085375,"total":0.00282765}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774815905476,"responseId":"msg_016wAzQXxLhEEpcaKhQMxvj8"}}
{"type":"message","id":"bdbcc222","parentId":"522fa63d","timestamp":"2026-03-29T20:25:06.962Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_01QsW5MMo5YN3VRbfjwXXtZq","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Task Watchdog\n\nGlobal task registry + watchdog for Tobias long-running tasks.\n\n## Goal\n- track tasks launched by Tobias\n- check every 5 minutes\n- notify Lucca every 10 minutes while running\n- send final notification on completion/failure\n- stay silent when no tasks are active\n\n## Files\n- `config.json` — watchdog settings\n- `active_tasks.json` — active monitored tasks\n- `task_history.jsonl` — completed/failed task history\n- `watchdog.py` — deterministic status checker\n\n## Scope (MVP)\n- monitors Tobias-launched subagents first\n- stores global registry so it can work across chats/surfaces\n- internal timestamps are ISO; user-facing messages must be human formatted\n\n## Operational protocol (mandatory)\nFor every long-running subagent launched by Tobias:\n1. spawn the subagent\n2. immediately register it in `active_tasks.json`\n3. only after registration, confirm to Lucca that the task was launched\n\nRule:\n- spawn without register = incomplete launch\n- do not claim a task is being monitored unless it is already in the registry\n\n## Safety layers\nThe watchdog design uses three layers together:\n1. **Launch wrapper discipline** — spawn -> register -> confirm\n2. **No-confirmation-without-registry** — Tobias must not claim monitoring without persisted registration\n3. **Launch audit** — `watchdog_launch_audit.py` scans for recent unregistered subagent sessions and auto-registers them as a fallback safety net\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774815906962}}
{"type":"message","id":"4b14c796","parentId":"bdbcc222","timestamp":"2026-03-29T20:25:08.154Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now let me execute the watchdog script:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_016HSLxMFUA3hdxgDH77hBvD","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\task_watchdog\\watchdog.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-haiku-4-5","usage":{"input":6,"output":84,"cacheRead":15639,"cacheWrite":1135,"totalTokens":16864,"cost":{"input":0.000006,"output":0.00042,"cacheRead":0.0015639000000000002,"cacheWrite":0.00141875,"total":0.00340865}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774815906963,"responseId":"msg_012LELdSxBgypNtG3ZXjtRLL"}}
